    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "# Real-Time Threat Detection  \r\n\r\nThis chatbot has been fine-tuned to provide insights into **Real-Time Threat Detection** and its role in cybersecurity.  \r\n\r\n## Do This:\r\n\r\n### Explore AI in Security (Activity)\r\n- Interact with the chatbot to understand how **Real-Time Threat Detection** works and how it helps prevent cyber threats.  \r\n- Use the **Conversation Starters** below to guide your exploration:  \r\n   - **Solution Overview:** *How does Real-Time Threat Detection work?*  \r\n   - **Problem Addressed:** *What network vulnerabilities does it target?*  \r\n   - **Pros & Cons:** *What are the advantages and limitations of this solution?*  \r\n   - **Project Application:** *How could this be used to mitigate risks in my chosen company scenario?*  \r\n\r\n### Risk Assessment Application\r\n- Use the chatbot’s responses to refine your **Network Security Risk Assessment** by identifying how Real-Time Threat Detection could help **prevent, detect, and respond** to network vulnerabilities.  \r\n\r\n### Tip: \r\n- If the chatbot’s response is unclear, try **rephrasing your question** with more details for a **more targeted answer**.  \r\n",
