        "modelCardInfo": {
          "botName": "Real-Time Threat Detection Expert",
          "description": "This chatbot helps students explore Real-Time Threat Detection in cybersecurity. It explains how this AI-driven solution works, identifies the network vulnerabilities it mitigates, and provides insights on how to apply it in risk assessments.",
          "intendedUse": "Educational Purposes: Designed to assist students in understanding Real-Time Threat Detection and how it can be used to improve network security.\nProject Support: Helps students apply AI-driven security solutions to their Network Security Risk Assessments.\nGuided Exploration: Encourages students to ask structured questions and think critically about cybersecurity applications.",
          "limitationsAndWarnings": "Not a real cybersecurity tool: This chatbot provides educational insights only and should not be used for real-world security decisions.\nSimplified explanations: Responses are tailored for students and may not include full technical details used in professional cybersecurity.\nAI Limitations: The chatbot may occasionally provide overgeneralized answers or miss nuanced security concerns—students should verify information using their course materials.",
          "testingAndEvaluation": "Tested for clarity and accuracy in explaining Real-Time Threat Detection in an educational setting.\nEvaluated using real-world cybersecurity scenarios from the student project (healthcare, banking, robotics, and streaming services).\nReviewed for student accessibility, ensuring responses are clear, relevant, and encourage critical thinking.",
